{"tid":182501,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"10.5吋iPad Pro 可能在4月推出","createTime":"2017-04-01T11:36:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T03:17:51.000Z","uid":31208,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"22776f70a50cd5d97edec08057bff5bd7d23b85c","tid":182501,"uid":31208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T11:36:45.000Z","msg":"根據 IHS / Markit 分析師 Rhoda Alexander 表示，傳說中的 10.5 吋 iPad Pro 本月已開始小批量試產，但確切上市日期則還無法確定，6 月、9 月或更晚都有可能。(<a href=\"http://Forbes.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FForbes.com&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=5387120d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Forbes.com</a>)<br />\n<br />\nMac Otakara 先前報導 10.5 吋 iPad Pro 將在 3 月發表，但傳聞並未成真，最終僅有平價版 iPad 與 128GB 版 iPhone SE 於上周低調上市，蘋果連發表會也省了。<br />\n<br />\n最近的傳言指向 iPad Pro 可能在 4 月推出，藉以配合蘋果新總部落成啟用，Alexander 不排除 4 月上市的可能性，但認為最初可能只會在美國與少數其他國家限量開賣，過段時間隨著產量增加，才會擴大上市國家。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://Macrumors.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMacrumors.com&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=9d39cfd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Macrumors.com</a> 引述知情人士消息報導亦指出，雖然蘋果沒有明說，但供應鏈非常清楚 10.5 吋 iPad Pro 上市時間已近在咫尺，最快或許是 4 月。"},{"pid":"29f110b62ba3e9624d41f0eaddc7891983425094","tid":182501,"uid":12804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T12:11:49.000Z","msg":"好多可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2f1d16ad066aca312d7f4f149dff92ead4329e7","tid":182501,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T12:15:14.000Z","msg":"呢d分色c新聞iphone4吹到而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afd777453a43b4ac269cda74ef46fe385094e89c","tid":182501,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T12:16:45.000Z","msg":"仲衰過 支爆"},{"pid":"4d578873f4a9e648d6ca80af01e43ad6841bbaea","tid":182501,"uid":19789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T12:27:48.000Z","msg":"用緊pro 9.7+筆+kb<br />\n如果10.5符合以下嘅條件，我會昇：<br />\n1. 用得番哂所有舊配件（因為好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n2. 冇加價or even減價（然後我會買256）<br />\n3. 3D touch<br />\n4. 個OS有改善（file management）<br />\n5. A10X<br />\n6. 更高resolution<br />\n7. 3GB RAM or above<br />\n<br />\n其他：<br />\n1. touch ID 2<br />\n2. 防水<br />\n3. 唔突鏡頭"},{"pid":"c737cede77ab4c9f24b51e04b5ff114fd568f7cf","tid":182501,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T17:45:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用緊pro 9.7+筆+kb<br />\n如果10.5符合以下嘅條件，我會昇：<br />\n1. 用得番哂所有舊配件（因為好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n2. 冇加價or even減價（然後我會買256）<br />\n3. 3D touch<br />\n4. 個OS有改善（file management）<br />\n5. A10X<br />\n6. 更高resolution<br />\n7. 3GB RAM or above<br />\n<br />\n其他：<br />\n1. touch ID 2<br />\n2. 防水<br />\n3. 唔突鏡頭</blockquote><br />\nIpad啲尺寸而家越出越多餘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根本而家有呢三個尺寸已經非常夠用"},{"pid":"316ea878ea5e00ef41b331c6be3ba61ae8b8091e","tid":182501,"uid":24293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T18:45:28.000Z","msg":"其實大唔大機會今個月出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91ef048661cf7ded81f98e4eabf214ccf2398fec","tid":182501,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T18:47:32.000Z","msg":"屌你咩Apple<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出到啲版本亂到開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c42e2d863748efb08d9ff6ed632381324e624923","tid":182501,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T19:11:26.000Z","msg":"其實點解要有10.5<br />\n係取代9.7 定係新加?"},{"pid":"8ce19e2c25f0aee320c301602a739545bec0946f","tid":182501,"uid":83012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T19:15:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實點解要有10.5<br />\n係取代9.7 定係新加?</blockquote><br />\n新加，現時擁有尺寸9.7 10.5 12.9，即將淘汰7.9<br />\nBTW 比我係Tim，一定會保留7.9 9.7 12.9，Mini size出街真係好撚正"},{"pid":"fa4d6963aacc101d904ed6239de681d6596e2a13","tid":182501,"uid":19789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T00:31:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實點解要有10.5<br />\n係取代9.7 定係新加?</blockquote><br />\n新加，現時擁有尺寸9.7 10.5 12.9，即將淘汰7.9<br />\nBTW 比我係Tim，一定會保留7.9 9.7 12.9，Mini size出街真係好撚正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMacBook<br />\n11 (air，已收檔)<br />\n12<br />\n13 (air/pro，air就收檔)<br />\n15 (pro)<br />\n<br />\niPad <br />\n7.9 (貌似要收檔)<br />\n9.7 (2017/pro，傳pro會變10.5)<br />\n10.5 (傳聞會出，取代9.7pro)<br />\n12.9 (pro)<br />\n<br />\n如果以上全部成真<br />\nMacBook就有12/13/15<br />\niPad就有9.7/10.5/12.9"},{"pid":"b6aefdd07e1bce2bc845eb67a5f35269e5ea3c7e","tid":182501,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T01:09:42.000Z","msg":"係咪印度生產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba926eba116d857ede49c765493f8d83f6566f38","tid":182501,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:01:42.000Z","msg":"究竟幾時出呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97b719f34bf067cc871cf139dff6fd26f9b0cf15","tid":182501,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:02:00.000Z","msg":"等到好苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d5580691b4bfb33a15d75ad275a7f702e7eaf8","tid":182501,"uid":435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T19:22:00.000Z","msg":"改resolution <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad0c3af7424e54deb394de0e4d19c524300d663","tid":182501,"uid":2668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T20:04:59.000Z","msg":"到底點解仲要係兩隻pro 中間加個size<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgm